        "content": "<p>There are two distinct questions --construction of the algebro-geometric projective space and the differential-geometric one. Neither implies the other (until we have the analyticification functor, and even then it will be some work proving that the analyticification of the algebro-geometric object is diffeomorphic to the differential geometic one). I think Kenny is concerned with the algebraic geometry construction.</p>",
